snippet.title: Cosmic Crunch Trailer (BUAS Year 2 project)
snippet.description:
A game we had to make in 2 weeks as a team out of 10 people, but we also had to make a custom controller for it.

Product owner:
Tomek Sierko

Designers:
Sven de Wit
Norbert van Hamond
Ronny Josch

Programmers:
Joey Jacobs (Also did the background music)
Jonah Rutten

Artists:
Luuk Ammerlaan
Naeema Saeed
Coen Oorschot
Laura Bot
